<br>
Just because your an anti doesn't mean you have pvp. Basicly verant didn't give us teams so we formed out own.  Working together is an absolute neccesity for survival on a pvp server.<br>
<br>
The goal of anyone interested at all in pvp is to die as little as possible and give as many opposing people free trips to their bind point as possible.  One way to work together to get this done is to group up in guilds but this isn't sufficient because your guildies aren't always around.  Whats needed is a large scale group like a race team.  Well we don't have one of those sooo all the antis basicly form a single team.<br>
<br>
What can a large scale team do that a guild can't? Remember RZ is fragmented into a lot of smaller guilds rather than the larger guilds that are common on TZ and VZ. A large scale team has the resources to get something done.  There may be 1 fusion, 1 knights errant, 2 black daggers and so on in a given zone but cooperatively as member of a larger team (the anti pks) This group can control the zone they want to hunt in, remove the pks when they invade, and kick their asses.<br>
<br>
If they remain neutral and do not interfere in pvp one way or the other what happens to them? What happens is a group of pks moves in picking off one person after another individually.<br>
<br>
Aside from the that there is a definate us vs them mentality that is only natural given there has never been any acceptable type of pvp unlike on teams where race on race pvp is expected.  Because there is no accepted form of pvp all of it has been lumped together as ganking by most.  <br>
<br>
The naked wizard attacking the injured melee has become the symbol of all RZ pvp and that is a sad thing.<br>
<br>
The fact that there is so much bad feeling asociated with pking  results in less non lamers than ever pking which leads to even more hatred towards those that remain because a larger and larger percentage of them do fit that stereotype described above and so on. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhawkmoth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hawkmoth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/12/02 4:19:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=578.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hiv's cheat/exploit policy</span><hr size=1> Derail my thread will you! /spank<br>
